---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ImmersiveRealmMap from '../components/ImmersiveRealmMap.astro';
import realms from '../data/realms.json';
import atlasHotspots from '../data/atlas-hotspots.json';
import { guardianRoster } from '../lib/guardians.js';

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
const realmsBySlug = new Map(realms.map((realm) => [realm.slug, realm]));
const guardiansByRealm = new Map(guardianRoster.map((guardian) => [guardian.realmSlug, guardian]));
const atlasEntries = atlasHotspots.map((hotspot) => {
  const realm = realmsBySlug.get(hotspot.realmSlug);
  const guardian = guardiansByRealm.get(hotspot.realmSlug);

  if (!realm || !guardian) {
    throw new Error(`Atlas sem dados para o reino: ${hotspot.realmSlug}`);
  }

  return { ...hotspot, realm, guardian };
});
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Atlas Imersivo do Continente — Realm of Crests"
  description="Explore o Mapa Canônico de Realm of Crests: dezenove Reinos, seus Guardiões, Essências, Fervores e cicatrizes territoriais."
>
  <section
    class="atlas-prologue"
    aria-labelledby="atlas-page-title"
    style={`--atlas-map-url: url("${base}/assets/maps/map_continent.webp")`}
  >
    <div class="atlas-prologue-glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="wide-wrap atlas-prologue-inner">
      <span class="rubric">arquivo cartográfico · instrumento de exploração</span>
      <h1 id="atlas-page-title">O MUNDO NÃO SE ENTREGA<br /><span>ELE É DESCOBERTO</span></h1>
      <p>
        Cada fronteira guarda uma vontade. Cada rota cobra memória. Escolha um selo no mapa
        e deixe o continente revelar o Reino que existe sob ele.
      </p>
      <a href="#atlas-explorer">Adentrar o Atlas <span aria-hidden="true">↓</span></a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="wide-wrap atlas-experience-wrap">
    <ImmersiveRealmMap entries={atlasEntries} base={base} />
  </div>

  <section class="atlas-lore-sequence" aria-labelledby="atlas-lore-title">
    <div class="wrap">
      <header class="atlas-lore-heading" data-lore-reveal>
        <span class="rubric">três leis para atravessar o continente</span>
        <h2 id="atlas-lore-title">A CARTOGRAFIA TAMBÉM É LORE</h2>
        <p>O mapa não ilustra apenas lugares. Ele registra forças que governam toda travessia.</p>
      </header>

      <div class="atlas-lore-path">
        <article class="atlas-lore-chapter ancestral" data-lore-reveal>
          <span class="atlas-lore-number">I</span>
          <div>
            <span class="rubric">origem</span>
            <h3>SOLO ANCESTRAL</h3>
            <p>Primeiro espaço de existência do Realm. Nenhum Reino o reivindica sozinho porque todos nasceram de sua memória.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="atlas-lore-chapter sacred" data-lore-reveal>
          <span class="atlas-lore-number">II</span>
          <div>
            <span class="rubric">travessia</span>
            <h3>CAMINHOS SAGRADOS</h3>
            <p>Veias ontológicas abertas pela ressonância antiga. Reduzem o custo da jornada, mas nunca anulam a distância.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="atlas-lore-chapter ruin" data-lore-reveal>
          <span class="atlas-lore-number">III</span>
          <div>
            <span class="rubric">limite</span>
            <h3>FRONTEIRA DA RUÍNA</h3>
            <p>Onde a realidade física enfraquece e a memória apodrece. Os ecos se perdem; a orientação deixa de ser promessa.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>

      <aside class="atlas-route-law" data-lore-reveal>
        <span class="rubric">regra de governança cartográfica</span>
        <p>Distância canônica é sempre medida por rota, nunca em linha reta.</p>
      </aside>

      <p class="atlas-source rubric">fontes: mapa canônico do continente v1.0 · índice de mapas, escala e rotas v1.1 · revisão canônica: 2026-07-11</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<script>
  function bindAtlasLoreReveal() {
    const chapters = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll<HTMLElement>('[data-lore-reveal]:not(.is-revealed)'));
    if (!chapters.length) return;
    if (window.matchMedia('(prefers-reduced-motion: reduce)').matches) {
      chapters.forEach((chapter) => chapter.classList.add('is-revealed'));
      return;
    }
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach((entry) => {
        if (!entry.isIntersecting) return;
        entry.target.classList.add('is-revealed');
        observer.unobserve(entry.target);
      });
    }, { threshold: .18 });
    chapters.forEach((chapter) => observer.observe(chapter));
  }

  document.addEventListener('astro:page-load', bindAtlasLoreReveal);
</script>

<style>
  .atlas-prologue {
    position: relative;
    display: grid;
    min-height: min(58vh, 620px);
    place-items: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201, 163, 92, .22);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .atlas-prologue::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(12,10,8,.94), rgba(12,10,8,.42) 48%, var(--ink)),
      var(--atlas-map-url) center 43% / cover;
    filter: saturate(.72);
    transform: scale(1.035);
  }

  .atlas-prologue-glow {
    position: absolute;
    width: min(42vw, 540px);
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(226,183,107,.18), rgba(226,183,107,.04) 36%, transparent 68%);
    mix-blend-mode: screen;
    animation: prologue-breathe 5s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }

  @keyframes prologue-breathe { to { transform: scale(1.12); opacity: .72; } }

  .atlas-prologue-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; padding-block: 4rem 5.5rem; }
  .atlas-prologue .rubric { display: block; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; color: var(--gold); }
  .atlas-prologue h1 { color: var(--parchment); font-size: clamp(2rem, 5.8vw, 4.5rem); letter-spacing: .105em; text-shadow: 0 8px 34px #000; }
  .atlas-prologue h1 span { color: var(--gold); }
  .atlas-prologue p { max-width: 58ch; margin: 1.5rem auto 0; color: var(--parchment); font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.7vw, 1.2rem); font-style: italic; text-shadow: 0 2px 12px #000; }
  .atlas-prologue a { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: .7rem; margin-top: 1.6rem; padding: .72rem 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gold); color: var(--gold); font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: .62rem; letter-spacing: .18em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .atlas-prologue a:hover { color: var(--parchment); border-color: var(--parchment); }

  .atlas-experience-wrap { position: relative; z-index: 2; margin-top: clamp(-3.7rem, -5vw, -2rem); }

  .atlas-lore-sequence { padding-block: clamp(5rem, 9vw, 8rem); }
  .atlas-lore-heading { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 3rem; text-align: center; }
  .atlas-lore-heading .rubric { color: var(--gold); }
  .atlas-lore-heading h2 { margin-top: .85rem; color: var(--parchment); font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 4vw, 2.7rem); }
  .atlas-lore-heading p { margin: 1rem auto 0; color: var(--parchment-dim); font-style: italic; }

  .atlas-lore-path { position: relative; max-width: 850px; margin-inline: auto; }
  .atlas-lore-path::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 2rem; bottom: 2rem; left: 34px; width: 1px; background: linear-gradient(var(--gold), var(--amber), var(--crimson)); opacity: .55; }
  .atlas-lore-chapter { position: relative; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 68px 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; align-items: start; padding: 2rem 0; }
  .atlas-lore-number { position: relative; z-index: 1; display: grid; width: 68px; height: 68px; place-items: center; border: 1px solid rgba(201,163,92,.5); border-radius: 50%; color: var(--gold); background: var(--ink); font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: .8rem; box-shadow: 0 0 28px rgba(201,163,92,.12); }
  .atlas-lore-chapter > div { padding: .2rem 0 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--edge); }
  .atlas-lore-chapter .rubric { display: block; margin-bottom: .4rem; }
  .atlas-lore-chapter h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; letter-spacing: .16em; }
  .atlas-lore-chapter p { max-width: 64ch; margin: .7rem 0 0; color: var(--parchment-dim); }
  .atlas-lore-chapter.sacred h3 { color: var(--amber); }
  .atlas-lore-chapter.ruin h3 { color: #b85b89; }

  .atlas-route-law { max-width: 850px; margin: 2.5rem auto 0; padding: 1.3rem 1.5rem; border: 1px solid rgba(201,163,92,.36); background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(201,163,92,.08), transparent); text-align: center; }
  .atlas-route-law .rubric { color: var(--gold); }
  .atlas-route-law p { margin: .45rem 0 0; color: var(--parchment); font-size: 1.12rem; font-style: italic; }
  .atlas-source { margin: 2rem 0 0; color: var(--parchment-faint); font-size: .62rem; text-align: center; }

  [data-lore-reveal] { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); transition: opacity .7s ease, transform .7s ease; }
  [data-lore-reveal].is-revealed { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  .atlas-lore-chapter:nth-child(2) { transition-delay: .08s; }
  .atlas-lore-chapter:nth-child(3) { transition-delay: .16s; }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .atlas-prologue { min-height: 480px; }
    .atlas-prologue::before { background-position: 52% center; }
    .atlas-prologue-inner { padding-block: 3rem 5rem; }
    .atlas-prologue h1 br { display: none; }
    .atlas-experience-wrap { width: calc(100% - 1rem); margin-top: -2.5rem; }
    .atlas-lore-path::before { left: 24px; }
    .atlas-lore-chapter { grid-template-columns: 48px 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
    .atlas-lore-number { width: 48px; height: 48px; }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .atlas-prologue-glow { animation: none; }
    [data-lore-reveal] { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
  }
</style>
